It is also mishandling and [[Corruption in Papua New Guinea|corruption showcase]].<ref>Chris Lang [https://redd-monitor.org/2009/06/07/anatomy-of-a-deal-the-april-salome-redd-project-in-papua-new-guinea/ Anatomy of a deal: The April Salome REDD project in Papua New Guinea.]</ref><ref name="filer">Colin Filer ''[http://www.jstor.org/stable/j.ctt183q3k6.13. How April Salumei Became the REDD Queen.]'' In ''Tropical Forests Of Oceania: Anthropological Perspectives'', edited by FILER COLIN, BELL JOSHUA A., and WEST PAIGE, 179-210. Australia: ANU Press, 2015. </ref> <ref>[https://www.greenpeace.org/japan/Global/japan/press/releases/attached/redd.pdf Papua New Guinea: not ready for REED]</ref><ref>[http://www.ecodaily.org/featured/some-questions-for-stephen-hooper-about-the-carbon-benefit-units-sold-from-his-april-salumei-redd-project-in-papua-new-guinea/ Some Questions for Stephen Hooper About The “Carbon Benefit Units” Sold from His April Salumei REDD Project in Papua New Guinea] EcoDaily October 5, 2017</ref>
